  <h2>The Polk County HVAC company that will actually drive out to Lakeland, Winter Haven &amp; Lake Wales</h2>
  <p>Most of the big Tampa HVAC companies won't cross the Hillsborough–Polk line. We do. I Care Air Care has been driving from our Wesley Chapel HQ into Polk County for more than sixteen years — Lakeland, Winter Haven, Bartow, Auburndale, Haines City, Davenport, Poinciana, Lake Wales — and charging the same flat rates we charge in our own backyard.</p>
  <p>Polk is a different HVAC environment from coastal Tampa. Higher summer design temps, real winter freezes, more rural service calls, more mobile and manufactured homes, a booming short-term-rental market in the <strong>Four Corners / ChampionsGate</strong> corridor, and a citrus-belt microclimate with fog and freeze cycles that punish electrical components. We build our service specs around those realities, not a generic Tampa Bay template.</p>

  <h2>HVAC services we provide in Polk County</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><a href="/services/ac-repair-tampa/"><strong>AC repair</strong></a> — capacitor, contactor, blower motor, fan motor, refrigerant, thermostat and compressor diagnostics across every Polk ZIP.</li>
    <li><a href="/services/emergency-ac-repair-tampa/"><strong>Urgent AC repair</strong></a> — priority scheduling for Polk vacation rentals, 55+ communities, and medical-needs households when cooling is out.</li>
    <li><a href="/services/hvac-installation-tampa/"><strong>HVAC installation</strong></a> — Manual-J sized to Polk design temps with Polk County or City of Lakeland permit handling.</li>
    <li><a href="/services/ac-maintenance-tampa/"><strong>AC maintenance &amp; tune-ups</strong></a> — 21-point seasonal service with Polk-specific freeze-protection configuration each fall.</li>
    <li><a href="/services/air-duct-cleaning-tampa/"><strong>Air duct cleaning</strong></a> — HEPA-based rotary brush + antimicrobial. Heavy pollen belts around Lake Wales and Bartow citrus groves make this routine here.</li>
    <li><a href="/services/heating-services-tampa/"><strong>Heating services</strong></a> — heat-pump repair, auxiliary heat strips, and gas furnace service in older Lakeland and Bartow homes.</li>
    <li><a href="/services/thermostat-installation-tampa/"><strong>Smart thermostat installation</strong></a> — Ecobee, Nest, Honeywell, with heat-pump-specific programming Polk winters actually need.</li>
    <li><a href="/services/refrigeration-repair-tampa/"><strong>Commercial refrigeration</strong></a> — Lakeland restaurants, Winter Haven cafes, and vacation-rental-area convenience stores.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Short-term rentals: Davenport, ChampionsGate &amp; the Four Corners corridor</h2>
  <p>The US-27 corridor through Davenport, ChampionsGate, Solterra and Four Corners is one of the heaviest short-term-rental markets in the country. That means HVAC systems that never rest, absentee owners, and emergency calls that hit the property manager at 9pm. We handle a large slate of rental-property service contracts here: after-hours dispatch, direct invoicing to the owner or management company, photo-documented repairs, and access via smart-lock or lockbox code. If your rental is losing a star on every guest review because of AC issues, call us — that's a solvable problem.</p>

  <h2>Lakeland, Winter Haven &amp; Bartow core: older housing stock, heavier sizing</h2>
  <p>The historic core of Polk — <strong>Lakeland's Dixieland, Cleveland Heights, Lake Hollingsworth; Winter Haven's Lake Region and Lake Elbert; Bartow's downtown historic district</strong> — is mostly 1940s–1970s construction with ducts in unconditioned attics running at 140°F on a summer afternoon. Replacing the condenser on one of these homes without sealing the ducts is the most common waste of money we see. Our replacement proposals include duct inspection, sealing, and often partial replacement in older Polk homes.</p>

  <h2>55+ communities: Solivita, Crescent Lakes &amp; Lake Ashton</h2>
  <p>Polk has some of the largest 55+ communities in Florida — <strong>Solivita (Poinciana), Lake Ashton (Winter Haven / Lake Wales), Lakeside Estates, Lake Region Village</strong>. We do a lot of service in these communities and we approach it differently: we explain what we find in plain language, we don't upsell, we leave written quotes family members can review, and we coordinate service with community office hours or gate access codes. Tim's personal cell goes in the service record for any resident who asks.</p>

  <h2>Polk-specific freeze protection for heat pumps</h2>
  <p>Polk's 2–5 freeze events per winter are real, and they damage heat-pump systems installed with factory-default lock-out temps. We manually configure lock-out temperatures (typically 32–35°F), verify defrost-cycle behavior, and size supplemental electric heat strips to your home's heat-loss calc — so you don't wake up to a 58°F house during a January cold snap. This is a 15-minute adjustment most contractors skip; we do it on every Polk install and as part of any fall tune-up.</p>

